  "text": "Coming back to the discussion in Sec. 2.3, let us observe, following [CITATION_1] , that, if we impose only vector superfield equation, Eq. (21), then, as a result of (11), the complex scalar main superfield R, which is chiral due to (10), also obeys D α R = 0; hence it becomes equal to a (complex) constant,",
